Dialogue: 5,0:00:10.73,0:00:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:11.81,0:00:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hizuru!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:14.18,0:00:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, yer alive again!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:19.17,0:00:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Nezu! Lemme explain!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:21.46,0:00:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kofune's daughter who died yesterday!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.50,0:00:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer with the shadows after all!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.47,0:00:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Nezu. Don't rush to judgment.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:32.87,0:00:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I died?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:36.82,0:00:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:40.63,0:00:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:42.49,0:00:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The world you observe becomes reality.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:45.46,0:00:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The four-armed shadow said that?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:47.58,0:00:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:49.17,0:00:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But why do I have that power?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If your right eye belonged to Haine,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:57.70,0:01:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,then that eye is made of shadows.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:01.75,0:01:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't remember when it was printed?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:04.72,0:01:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:07.03,0:01:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but probably after I came back to the island.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:12.18,0:01:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Every piece fits now.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.32,0:01:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who gave that eye to Ajiro Shinpei was you, Ushio.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:20.58,0:01:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Me?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:22.16,0:01:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:25.61,0:01:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think you failed the last loop?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:29.03,0:01:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing was acting separately from y'all after defeating Mio's shadow.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:35.47,0:01:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, we need to work together.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:38.82,0:01:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 5,0:01:39.59,0:01:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:41.44,0:01:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hizuru!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:58.55,0:02:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That was...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:00.45,0:02:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezu, Ushio is an ally.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:03.15,0:02:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She was our ally till the end.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.24,0:02:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ms. Nagumo. Can ya hear me?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:08.76,0:02:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we have that message and Shinpei's right eye here.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:14.24,0:02:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust you.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.71,0:02:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Nagumo...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.92,0:02:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's human nature to believe in fiction.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.25,0:02:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it be riches, religion, or stories.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.81,0:02:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm a novelist.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:29.32,0:02:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't fictional.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.07,0:02:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:33.52,0:02:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the first time I saw her smile.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:37.29,0:02:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So yer risking yer lives too?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.00,0:02:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the four-armed shadow trying to revive Haine?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:46.21,0:02:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It fed a lot of people to Haine at the summer festival.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.20,0:02:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happens after that.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.04,0:02:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about an "Ending."
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.49,0:03:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That massive body is Hiruko's true form.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.78,0:03:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If the shadow at Shiori's feet is just part of that,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.09,0:03:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it explains why we couldn't kill Shiori no matter what.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.82,0:03:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But Shiori ain't very strong.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:11.95,0:03:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All she can do is walk around.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.75,0:03:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiruko's too weak to leave the cave.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.20,0:03:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this how it works?
