Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.95,0:03:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your plan?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.05,0:03:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to go underground now and defeat the true form,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.64,0:03:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but if we can't defeat the four-armed shadow, \Nit'll end up like the last loop.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:39.84,0:03:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of all, I'm worried about Mio.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.13,0:03:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a plan fer Sou and his family too.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.42,0:03:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I want us to capture Shiori at Koba Mart like last time.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.88,0:03:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya can't kill her, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.06,0:03:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of capturing her?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.56,0:03:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer right,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:58.64,0:04:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but I might be able to erase her.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.97,0:04:00.97,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:20.29,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}It's come to the point where I just want to hoard all your words
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:26.26,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Even the ramblings from your travels are treasures to me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:29.44,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Whether I sketch or erase it's all torn away
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:32.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}That's the price I pay for my awakening
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:38.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Or my daydream's tricking me and I'm still lost in the unknown
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:41.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Illuminated by the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:44.89,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Your figure casts a shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:48.02,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}And when that silhouette wavers slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:50.85,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}That happens to be my cue
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:57.82,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}I wish this were fiction but slow motion is how it begins
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:05:03.74,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}If the visceral warmth and traces you left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:09.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Are protecting someone's future, I'll play the warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:13.46,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Amidst pain and sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:16.46,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}I'll conquer my fears
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:19.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}It's a paradox of life
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:21.97,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Or perhaps god's algorithm
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:25.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}When our tactics overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:30.48,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}We'll be laughing
