Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.33,0:05:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I feel better than I did yesterday.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.72,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Shin's back.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.14,0:05:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.43,0:05:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's wrong, Sou?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.21,0:05:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta talk to Dad about Ushio.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:00.72,0:06:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave. I don't have time for that.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.18,0:06:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sei!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.44,0:06:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about him.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.28,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Make some time fer him, will ya?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.76,0:06:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Negoro, take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.35,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:22.83,0:06:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to my room tonight at 10 o'clock.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.46,0:06:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll spare five minutes.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:30.92,0:06:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mom.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.90,0:06:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but what's this about?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.33,0:06:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing much.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.76,0:06:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.04,0:06:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ajiro Shinpei is looking into the shadow sickness.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.66,0:06:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.42,0:06:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Kofune Ushio, and now it's Minakata Hizuru.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.20,0:06:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are people sniffing around now?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.41,0:06:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's unlikely a coincidence that Minakata Hizuru returned.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.49,0:07:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ushio must've contacted Shinpei.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.40,0:07:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that Ushio's shadow wasn't erased and is now missing?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.39,0:07:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.96,0:07:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll find and erase it.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}First, we'll get to her family.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:15.48,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the entire Kofune family into shadows?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.80,0:07:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the plan.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Including Ajiro Shinpei.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.74,0:07:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.55,0:07:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, I'll be there.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.02,0:07:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello? My mother needs me. I must go.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama's boy.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.66,0:07:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, we have a report from Kinokawa City.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.21,0:07:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wakayama's seasonal treats are delicious...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.68,0:07:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're up, Ryuunosuke.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Erase Shiori?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.71,0:08:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In the last loop, I felt Haine coming in and trying to mess with my head.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.05,0:08:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe I can reverse that channel.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do the same?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.66,0:08:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it, but seems like it's worth trying.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.73,0:08:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.29,0:08:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to put her down myself, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.44,0:08:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezu told me last time.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:18.49,0:08:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuunosuke was killed by a shadow 14 years ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.06,0:08:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There were ligature marks on his neck.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.03,0:08:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Haine kill Ryuunosuke?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.00,0:08:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.98,0:08:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And she was my friend.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.16,0:08:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.73,0:08:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer friend?
