Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.87,0:08:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can talk more later.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:43.71,0:08:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna hear Mio's voice! Should I answer?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:46.97,0:08:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.55,0:08:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just joking.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.79,0:08:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:55.47,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(963,220)\fscx82\fscy82\frz5.19\fnLato\c&HA2A09E&\alpha&HD0&\blur10}Kofune Mio
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.51,0:08:55.47,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(963,220)\fscx82\fscy82\frz5.19\fnLato\c&HA2A09E&\blur1}Kofune Mio
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.94,0:08:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The phone is vibrating to tell me she's alive.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.78,0:08:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't let Mio die again.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.96,0:08:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hello? S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.35,0:09:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Repeating the previous actions should yield the same result.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.01,0:09:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In other words, we can capture Haine with Plan B.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.59,0:09:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haine is the one who took you and Asako from me.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.70,0:09:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it weren't for Haine, Kofune Ushio would still be alive, and so would a lot of other people.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's end this, Ryuunosuke.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.35,0:09:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that, Sis.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are ya ready?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.56,0:09:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was ready before ya were even born.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.14,0:09:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good to go.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.42,0:09:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Erase Haine,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.47,0:09:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}whom the four-armed treasures.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.39,0:09:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right here and now.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:45.05,0:09:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then we'll save everyone from the end of that summer festival.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:48.56,0:09:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi! Hizuru!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:50.49,0:09:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did I catch ya... I mean, you at dinner?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.31,0:09:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I had some gifts to give you.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.45,0:09:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Ya shouldn't've!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.97,0:10:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's looking.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya can come out, Ushio.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.29,0:10:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoopsie.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.43,0:10:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya transform, ya fight. Yer like a Precure.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.00,0:10:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my dream in kindergarten! It finally came true!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.33,0:10:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya know about Precure?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My granddaughter used to like it.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great, Shinpei.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.38,0:10:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.86,0:10:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized something amazing!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.26,0:10:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The nail gun that the four-armed shadow destroyed?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.84,0:10:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wow.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.23,0:10:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So this means...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.38,0:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,ya can bring the data ya scanned the last time to the next loop!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.34,0:10:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't it great?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.76,0:10:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.28,0:10:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer amazing, Ushio!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.95,0:11:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that outfit scanned last time too?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.77,0:11:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too bad, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish this wasn't damaged.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.50,0:11:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Should be fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.98,0:11:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I got the original.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.32,0:11:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nezu was holding two guns: \Nhis Nail Gun A and my Nail Gun B.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ushio rescans the data from Nail Gun B.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:27.88,signs,,0,0,0,,{=5}{\an7\move(0,0,104.33,0,21,5944)\c&HFBFBFC&\blur1\p1}m 710 81 l 1093 81 1093 174 710 174
