Dialogue: 2,0:11:21.91,0:11:27.88,signs,,0,0,0,,{=3}{\move(898,124,1002.33,124,21,5944)\fscx117\fscy117\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H4E4E4E&\blur0.7}Nail gun A
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:27.88,signs,,0,0,0,,{=2}{\an7\move(336,972,440.33,972,21,5944)\c&H262727&\blur1\p1}m -304 -54 l 300 -54 300 61 -304 61
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.91,0:11:27.88,signs,,0,0,0,,{=1}{\move(336,972,440.33,972,21,5944)\fscx97\fscy97\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&HE5E5E5&\alpha&HD0&\blur7.5}Nail gun B (shadow)
Dialogue: 2,0:11:21.91,0:11:27.88,signs,,0,0,0,,{=0}{\move(336,972,440.33,972,21,5944)\fscx97\fscy97\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&HE5E5E5&\blur0.6}Nail gun B (shadow)
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.53,0:11:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She overwrites the old data, then destroys the original.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.30,0:11:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.89,0:11:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I can use Nail Gun B again.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.88,0:11:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll put copying Nail Gun A on hold because Ushio's storage is full.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.40,0:11:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been five minutes since Ryuunosuke went in.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.74,0:11:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time he tells us to switch to Plan B.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.95,0:11:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.95,0:11:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then two minutes later,\N Shiori comes down from the balcony.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.90,0:11:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The third shot misses and she flees,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.37,0:11:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but I capture her by the green tea soft serve banner.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, I'll erase her.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.39,0:11:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.32,0:11:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we wait to hear from Ryuunosuke.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.05,0:12:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.03,0:12:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Run... away...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.13,0:12:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Nagu—
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.81,0:12:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.22,0:12:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no longer... like the... previous July 22nd...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.66,0:12:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're all together.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.02,0:12:34.02,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:37.11,title,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\c&HC0A038&\blur7}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.02,0:12:37.11,title,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.58,0:12:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hizuru!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:36.77,0:12:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It can't be.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.09,0:12:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are ya here?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.09,0:12:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't play fair, Shinpei.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.63,0:12:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did ya forget what I said back then?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.13,0:12:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Found ya."
Dialogue: 5,0:12:54.25,0:12:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a mark.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.06,0:13:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can find ya in any world ya go to.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.49,0:13:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.91,0:13:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been following ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:04.85,0:13:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't our eyes meet at the end of that summer festival?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.13,0:13:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can loop too.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.69,0:13:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew y'all would come here because \NI read Ryuunosuke's memory last time.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.81,0:13:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No... That can't be...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.43,0:13:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need two observers.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's either Mother...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:28.87,0:13:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,or you.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.81,0:13:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who survives will decide...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.81,0:13:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,which world is real!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.61,0:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill ya!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Three shots.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:42.38,0:13:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.85,0:13:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The three shots didn't stop him?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.57,0:13:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:57.69,0:14:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I scan everything, I'll disappear.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.04,0:14:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'll take that one arm!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.78,0:14:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.83,0:14:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was just a greeting, Ajiro Shinpei.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.72,0:14:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Loop as many times as ya like.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.86,0:14:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll find ya every time and seal that power away in the end.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.44,0:14:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haine!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.56,0:14:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was careless.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.70,0:14:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should've known that the enemy could have the same power as me.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:29.81,0:14:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haine also came from the summer festival.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.24,0:14:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My carelessness got those two killed.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio! Where's Ushio?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.44,0:14:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Did yer neck hurt?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:41.20,0:14:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to make it as quick as possible.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.47,0:14:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank goodness yer here, Ushio.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.55,0:14:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.75,0:14:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya did great.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, how're ya doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.86,0:14:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling good?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.20,0:14:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I could figure out who the four-armed shadow was,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.43,0:14:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was empty.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:58.69,0:15:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no data in it.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.77,0:15:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it even moving?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.19,0:15:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there was something weird.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.82,0:15:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It smelled just like Haine.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.50,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we win against an enemy who can loop?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.51,0:15:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine is most likely just using yer power to loop.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.95,0:15:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So she'll loop to the same starting point as us.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:19.84,0:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on even footing.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.86,0:15:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We can win. I know it!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.86,0:15:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.11,0:15:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:47.34,signs,,0,0,0,,{=9}{\move(1300,1058.28,1300,-116.73,20,4441)\fscx78\fscy78\fnPaint Hand\c&H968470&\alpha&HB0&\blur7.5}Bistro Kofune
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.88,0:15:47.34,signs,,0,0,0,,{=8}{\move(1300,1058.28,1300,-116.73,20,4441)\fscx78\fscy78\fnPaint Hand\c&H968470&\blur1.01}Bistro Kofune
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.38,0:15:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the starting point changed, when were we here?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is odd.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't be raining.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:51.75,0:15:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,July 22nd was sunny.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.82,0:15:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.35,0:15:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up fer a sec, Sis.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.87,0:16:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.63,0:16:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Nagumo?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:12.35,0:16:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking ain't gonna get us anywhere.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:14.06,0:16:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's follow 'em, Shinpei!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.65,0:16:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.91,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The setting changed?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.21,0:16:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It looks busy today.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.78,0:16:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Hizuru and Ryuunosuke.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.66,0:16:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it. Those two are Hizuru and her twin Ryuunosuke.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.52,0:16:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.53,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When I died the first time, something similar happened.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.60,0:16:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. Fer two?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.48,0:16:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are ya wearing an apron, Akemi?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.64,0:16:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Bistro Kofune's 10th anniversary,\N so everyone came by to eat here today.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.08,0:16:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Congrats!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.07,0:17:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. That's why I'm helping too.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mom?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:04.83,0:17:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really Akemi. Wow!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.58,0:17:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So this {\i1}is{\i0} the past.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:10.63,0:17:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 14 years ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:12.70,0:17:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When I died the first time, \NI was with Mio and the same thing happened.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.17,0:17:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was at the beach where ya died.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the past, and I saw everything.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.27,0:17:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That must've been Mio's memory.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.55,0:17:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then is this Ms. Nagumo's memory?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dessert's on us today!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.31,0:17:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.20,0:17:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like crowds, so I'm going home.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.68,0:17:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a sec!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:36.65,0:17:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Asako? Didn't see ya there.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:38.50,0:17:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a special day fer Bistro Kofune.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to celebrate together.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.30,0:17:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel the need to make a fuss to celebrate.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.30,0:17:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya don't need to go home, either!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.69,0:17:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ya have a heart?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.26,0:17:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm human, so I have a heart. But I want to leave.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.39,0:17:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Ms. Nagumo really hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.16,0:18:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy 10th anniversary, Bistro Kofune!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You should leave.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:08.17,0:18:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, if it ain't Hizuru.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.76,0:18:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya look so happy to see me.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:11.77,0:18:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.11,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tooru and Masahito. Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.47,0:18:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Those ten years sure went quick.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.95,0:18:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Alain, your food is always great.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:22.40,0:18:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't change.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.79,0:18:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did ya look in the mirror?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:27.33,0:18:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya haven't shaved! Yer hair is messy too.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.58,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I forgot.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:32.79,0:18:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer dad came too.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.40,0:18:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This must've been quite a day.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.67,0:18:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's amazing.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're moving.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.49,0:18:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their voices. Mannerisms.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.02,0:18:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how they were.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.56,0:18:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What jobs did yer parents do?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.76,0:18:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They were nautical archaeologists.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.81,0:18:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They dove underwater.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.39,0:18:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Masahito, so yer finally a priest.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.30,0:18:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I have a lot to learn, but I'm doing my best.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.17,0:19:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's new, Tooru?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.27,0:19:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about diving to that point I mentioned before.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.37,0:19:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitogashima has so much unique history.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:08.74,0:19:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I moved here.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.02,0:19:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The food here's great too.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.55,0:19:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ryuu. Why's Hizuru in a bad mood?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.24,0:19:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's actually my fault.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:24.02,0:19:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I never should've told ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:26.44,0:19:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.97,0:19:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She says she made a friend.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.03,0:19:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.60,0:19:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So I told her she's dreaming.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.82,0:19:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her it was an imaginary friend, and she got mad.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:41.35,0:19:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just mean.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:43.50,0:19:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I can't believe it either.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:44.97,0:19:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.56,0:19:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm joking. Sorry, Hizuru, I believe ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:48.54,0:19:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're joking?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:49.40,0:19:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need a joker to believe me.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:51.71,0:19:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Asa didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.72,0:19:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, Ryuu.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.63,0:19:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about yer friend.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:58.34,0:20:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We have less than 20 kids at school.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.66,0:20:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd ya meet someone new?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.29,0:20:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mt. Takanosu.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.76,0:20:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The setting changed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:15.24,signs,,0,0,0,,{=10}{\move(1498,189.79,1498,282.14,24,3694)\fscx73\fscy73\fnBrush Strokes\c&H141516&\1a&H10&\blur1.4}Hishigata Clinic
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.06,0:20:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei, this is...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:14.03,0:20:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The old Hishigata Clinic.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Was she really here?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she from the island?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.07,0:20:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.15,0:20:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya think so?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:24.52,0:20:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably not from our time.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.65,0:20:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get it once ya see her.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.58,0:20:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She usually appears around now.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:34.97,0:20:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.01,0:20:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The light on the second floor will turn on.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.28,0:20:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be a ghost.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:40.92,0:20:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too creepy!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.16,0:20:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear there are ghosts here.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.51,0:20:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see anyone.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.36,0:20:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Maybe she won't come today.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:59.32,0:21:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hizuru, we should head back.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:01.36,0:21:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Our parents will be worried.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.20,0:21:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be dangerous to go back once it gets dark.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:06.02,0:21:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised to meet her today.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:09.14,0:21:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep my promises.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hizuru!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:13.03,0:21:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take ya home, Asa.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:15.62,0:21:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis gets stubborn like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:44.80,0:21:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't be.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:47.74,0:21:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:50.40,0:21:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:55.00,0:21:55.00,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:22:01.64,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}All traces of you vanished into the sea breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:06.64,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6173A3&\3c&H22C3F8&\blur5\fad(200,200)}But even now I still see visions of you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:14.42,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HC3A644&\3c&HE9EBBB&\blur5\fad(200,200)}In reality I only have vivid memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.42,0:22:15.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HC3A644&\3c&HE9EBBB&\blur5\fad(200,0)}To play in my head over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:19.35,ED,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9AFAF8&\blur5\fad(0,200)}To play in my head over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:24.75,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6989A1&\3c&H73E97B&\blur5\fad(200,200)}Even if it's all just a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.75,0:22:28.87,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6989A1&\3c&H73E97B&\blur5\fad(200,200)}Please be close by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.17,0:22:31.93,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6A70EE&\3c&H83EF82&\blur5\fad(200,200)}Right next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:37.68,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE5D78D&\3c&HE4F4FB&\blur5\fad(200,200)}I fell for you before too long
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:40.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE5D78D&\3c&HE4F4FB&\blur5\fad(200,0)}But time alone was what progressed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.76,0:22:41.54,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&H59A599&\3c&HF8EAC3&\blur5\fad(0,200)}But time alone was what progressed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.05,0:22:46.03,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&H59A599&\3c&HF8EAC3&\blur5\fad(0,200)}I wanna go back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.33,0:22:55.02,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB67647&\3c&HD0C1AC&\blur5\fad(200,200)}I've listened to my share of heartbreak songs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:23:02.82,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB67647&\3c&HD0C1AC&\blur5\fad(200,200)}Spending my days torn up and crying but now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.82,0:23:05.37,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB67647&\3c&HD0C1AC&\blur5\fad(200,200)}I want to move on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:08.70,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB67647&\3c&HD0C1AC&\blur5\fad(200,0)}I shouldn't act tough and just finally be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:10.34,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HEBCEAB&\3c&HF4F3E8&\blur5\fad(0,200)}I shouldn't act tough and just finally be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:13.62,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HEBCEAB&\3c&HF4F3E8&\blur5\fad(0,200)}True to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.75,0:23:17.04,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HC16C32&\3c&HBFC385&\blur5\fad(200,0)}But it's too late for that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:19.66,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB4D1F0&\3c&HEAEEFD&\blur5\fad(0,200)}But it's too late for that
